data.description: Stunning 4 bedroom and 2 bathroom home nestled on a fenced 6,499 SqFt lot located on a peaceful cul-de-sac in sought after Enclave at Tapestry. The open-concept layout and high ceilings of this home provides large spaces with lots of natural light flowing through all the rooms. Large bedrooms with primary bedroom featuring an ensuite bathroom. This charming home boasts a large fenced backyard, providing privacy and room for outdoor activities. This home is being sold "as-is"
